==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Clairvoyance
<hw>Clair*voy"ance</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety>
<def>A power, attributed to some persons while in a mesmeric state, of
discerning objects not perceptible by the senses in their normal
condition.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Clairvoyant</ent>⟦br⟧
